  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16_1",
    "text": "1、气温与生活",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1199442119944212,
      0.18821980914774597,
      0.25755462575546256,
      0.2073050345508391
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16_2",
    "text": "(1) 气温：空气的温度，常用℃表示 日平均气温=一日内气温观测值之和÷观测次数 月平均气温二一月内日平均气温之和÷当月天数 年平均气温二一年内月平均气温之和÷月数(12)",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14225941422594143,
      0.21717670286278382,
      0.6685262668526267,
      0.3323461665021389
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16_3",
    "text": "(2)对人类活动的影响：气温影响人们的穿衣.饮食，住房.农业和交通等。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1403998140399814,
      0.3422178348140836,
      0.8414690841469085,
      0.3961829549193814
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16_4",
    "text": "2.气温的变化 (1)日变化",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11808461180846118,
      0.4060546232313261,
      0.27243142724314273,
      0.42645607107601186
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16_5",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14690841469084148,
      0.4376439618295492,
      0.24453742445374244,
      0.45672918723264233
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16_6",
    "text": "①概念：以一天为国期的气温变化 ②变化特点：一天当中最高气温出现在午后2点(4时)左右，最低气温出现在日出 前后。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10692701069270107,
      0.46791707798617965,
      0.9502556950255695,
      0.5521553142481079
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16_7",
    "text": "③气温日较差=最高气遍一最低气温",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1803812180381218,
      0.5613688713392563,
      0.5681078568107857,
      0.5824284304047384
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16_8",
    "text": "(2)年变化",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14783821478382148,
      0.5942744323790721,
      0.24360762436076244,
      0.6127015465613689
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16_9",
    "text": "①概念：以一年为周期的气温变化. ②变比特点：南北半球气温的变化正好相反 陆地上：北半球气温7月最高1月最低： 海洋上：北半球气温8月最高，2月最低。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.18317061831706183,
      0.6232313260941099,
      0.6378428637842863,
      0.7403751233958539
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16_10",
    "text": "③气温年较差 最高月平均气温一最低月平均气温.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.18688981868898186,
      0.7482724580454096,
      0.7178056717805672,
      0.7713063507732807
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_16_11",
    "text": "(3)通常用气温的变化曲线图来表示一个地方一年内的气温变化情况。 (4)气温年变化曲线图的绘制方法：一横月、二纵温.三定点、四连线",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
